  "notes": "0.1.36: QoL pass — 13 bug + UX fixes around the new MP3 player, friend system, and voice settings. Voice-only mode toggle now applies live mid-call. Friends modal closes on Esc, accepts @-prefixes, has type-ahead search. Per-peer volume slider clamped to actual range. Not-friends banner clears on view switch and on accept; gains a Block secondary action. Mp3 players auto-pause each other. Home rail shows a red dot when you have pending friend requests."
